channel.title: 317 Server
channel.description:
Well, Hello again guys, I need some more help, yeah I know I'm stupid, but I really need help, and even critizime is welcome, so all please post if you read this. I am i0wn3v3ry, I am creating my own server, but I ran into a bit of trouble, so I am asking for your help. Well, alot of my items are in the "weapon slot" when they are supposed to be in the cape slot, or another place, and I have no clue how to fix. Also, I am adding pvp armour, but when I do, I spawn and they are obby monsters when I put on, instead of a vesta plate or something, so any help is appreciated My armadyl godsword, doesen't have a special, and I have no clue were to get one, or add it at in my files. My other godswords all have stupid emotes for specials, so does anyone have realistic ones? Can anyone help me make a member zone, with member items, for members only? Can anyone help me add pvp armour that works? I can't upload to any sites ( I don't know why) I'm trying to increase some weapons, but I can't find a Item.Cfg, (server sided), I don't have an item.Cfg in server side, nor source side, because in source side, in my Item.java file, is where the items are placed. Where do I increase my stats for weapons/armour? Can anyone help me add real vengence? Does anyone know how to change the tele's from emote tab, to spell book, for ancients, lunar, and regular?
This is all for now, please help guys!
Add me at pritchardthomas@yahoo.com I have a teamviewer!
